This is a template geodata model to be used for modeling according CHBase, the "base modules of the Swiss Confederation for minimal geodata models".
Prepare your model according CHBase by importing the needed CHBase packages (i.e. modules) to your model.
Start modeling! Make sure to apply CHBase definitions wherever appropriate!
Questions? drop a line at "models@geo.admin.ch"
